Department of Neighborhoods Tree Fund could provide replacement trees for community planting projects in this MA. Strategies: Volunteers can help control minor invasive plant infestations and place and replenish wood chips under trees, activities with highly-visible results well-suited to large groups because they are labor-intensive but require no specialty skills.
